00:20:55.143 --> 00:20:56.143
educate.

00:20:56.143 --> 00:21:01.013
Now this is a good Sahaja Yogi who has been
in Sahaja Yoga for two three years, has been

00:21:01.013 --> 00:21:03.883
giving realizations to people but he doesn’t
have a job.

00:21:03.883 --> 00:21:10.123
It’s our duty in a way, to support his children
to be educated.

00:21:10.123 --> 00:21:13.243
See when this hand is self-supporting is all
right.

00:21:13.243 --> 00:21:17.472
I mean this is self-supporting is all right,
but in case it needs the support of this,

00:21:17.472 --> 00:21:24.753
this has to give the support.

00:21:24.753 --> 00:21:30.962
As we call scholarships or sometimes we call,
now we have got at least five or six children

00:21:30.962 --> 00:21:36.072
in our school there, who are absolutely free,
absolutely.

00:21:36.072 --> 00:21:41.503
Food, some of them I am supporting, some of
them Yogi’s supporting and some of them

00:21:41.503 --> 00:21:43.042
are absolutely free, absolutely hundred percent.

00:21:43.042 --> 00:21:46.773
Will not tell you the names.

00:21:46.773 --> 00:21:51.863
Their food their clothes everything and nobody
knows.

00:21:51.863 --> 00:21:57.312
We don’t want them to develop a feeling
[INAUDIBLE around?].

00:21:57.312 --> 00:22:03.462
So all the time, to be very calculating about
things is bad.

00:22:03.462 --> 00:22:10.552
I’ve seen a complete, manifesto typed [INAUDIBLE]
I don’t know what, about having a committee

00:22:10.552 --> 00:22:14.743
on top of this little preschool.

00:22:14.743 --> 00:22:16.143
That is not proper.

00:22:16.143 --> 00:22:22.613
It’s conditioning, everything, even if you
have to put these, balloons you’ll have

00:22:22.613 --> 00:22:24.773
a committee.

00:22:24.773 --> 00:22:31.363
This committee on top of that another committee
another.

00:22:31.363 --> 00:22:38.283
Trust, trust and trust.

00:22:38.283 --> 00:22:43.962
We have now one committee I had to do it,
is called as the finance committee all right.

00:22:43.962 --> 00:22:51.103
They are all audits, experts and accountants
and they will be here in Sydney.

00:22:51.103 --> 00:22:55.672
That doesn’t mean Sydney is dominating as
someone.

00:22:55.672 --> 00:23:02.472
Some subjects have to be central, as in any
government.

00:23:02.472 --> 00:23:08.373
That you should understand, and that these
can go and see your accounts if they’re

00:23:08.373 --> 00:23:12.753
all right or not.

00:23:12.753 --> 00:23:22.523
But nobody has to dominate in Sahaja Yoga,
we have to help support and trust.

00:23:22.523 --> 00:23:28.942
Now in this preschool I find there are only
seven children of that age group who are studying.

00:23:28.942 --> 00:23:31.462
There are smaller children also.

00:23:31.462 --> 00:23:37.832
I have suggested to him that why not use this
area for the school there’s a school there.

00:23:37.832 --> 00:23:41.253
And I would like children to be in My Room
than anybody else.

00:23:41.253 --> 00:23:43.623
So use this.

00:23:43.623 --> 00:23:48.613
You save money like that and children will
feel comforted.

00:23:48.613 --> 00:23:54.753
Everybody should see if they have time what
can I do for children, can I come and help

00:23:54.753 --> 00:23:55.753
you.

00:23:55.753 --> 00:23:59.722
Instead of that, how much money you spend
this that.

00:23:59.722 --> 00:24:03.842
You see there’s no income tax in Sahaja
Yoga, is there?

00:24:03.842 --> 00:24:07.402
We want to get rid of these kind of things.

00:24:07.402 --> 00:24:11.942
Everybody feels frightened and insecure, all
the time.

00:24:11.942 --> 00:24:14.103
Forget about these things.

00:24:14.103 --> 00:24:15.103
Trust.

00:24:15.103 --> 00:24:21.222
You don’t know how many thousands of dollars
I’ve lost, by trusting people.

00:24:21.222 --> 00:24:22.222
Thousands.

00:24:22.222 --> 00:24:24.812
But we have to trust.

00:24:24.812 --> 00:24:26.802
What can you do?

00:24:26.802 --> 00:24:29.783
We have to pay for our principles.

00:24:29.783 --> 00:24:37.903
The main principle is trusting and not to
ask about money where is what what is right.

00:24:37.903 --> 00:24:43.432
The second is a very bad situation here is,
because every parent can go and interfere

00:24:43.432 --> 00:24:44.432
with the teacher.

00:24:44.432 --> 00:24:47.072
Because they think they are paying for it.

00:24:47.072 --> 00:24:50.493
You’ll spoil your children completely.

00:24:50.493 --> 00:24:59.562
Should never never interfere with the teachers,
never.

00:24:59.562 --> 00:25:05.233
With the school.

00:25:05.233 --> 00:25:10.243
I mean if you don’t have money all right.

00:25:10.243 --> 00:25:15.883
Again you can have a committee, to find out
if they really don’t have money or not.

00:25:15.883 --> 00:25:20.383
But if somebody says I have no money I have
no job all right.

00:25:20.383 --> 00:25:27.682
Somebody should help them But it should not
be a kind of a police force behind these teachers,

00:25:27.682 --> 00:25:30.782
or behind the school or behind the leader.

00:25:30.782 --> 00:25:34.013
Where is the money gone where is that gone
this that?

00:25:34.013 --> 00:25:38.243
Those who worry too much of money will never
have money I tell you.

00:25:38.243 --> 00:25:46.503
Though I lose money quite a lot, but I get
double I tell you, never a problem.

00:25:46.503 --> 00:25:51.312
I never have a problem of money, never never
never.

00:25:51.312 --> 00:25:53.442
One must trust.

00:25:53.442 --> 00:26:01.603
I’ll tell you one example, very nice example,
which shows how Sahaja Yoga works out things.

00:26:01.603 --> 00:26:09.143
I went down to Rome, and we wanted to start
a school in Rome.

00:26:09.143 --> 00:26:16.782
We saw the land everything is very nice, but
we had to deposit the money immediately.

00:26:16.782 --> 00:26:23.513
And Guido said: ‘Mother we need about sixteen
thousand pounds worth of liras to deposit

00:26:23.513 --> 00:26:24.513
this’.

00:26:24.513 --> 00:26:29.312
I said: ‘I don’t know if I have that money
with Me in the bank or not.

00:26:29.312 --> 00:26:31.972
I’ll have to see, but doesn’t matter’.

00:26:31.972 --> 00:26:35.672
I reached the airport and I was leaving.

00:26:35.672 --> 00:26:41.523
Suddenly, Sandra came with a packet and she
said: ‘Mother this I have saved for You’.

00:26:41.523 --> 00:26:45.452
I said: ‘What is this?’

00:26:45.452 --> 00:26:46.782
‘This is money, liras’.

00:26:46.782 --> 00:26:53.353
I said: ‘But why I don’t need I don’t
take any money why why do you give Me?’.

00:26:53.353 --> 00:26:54.942
Suddenly it struck Me.

00:26:54.942 --> 00:26:57.603
‘How much it is?

00:26:57.603 --> 00:26:58.603
What is the value?’

00:26:58.603 --> 00:27:00.233
She said: ‘Sixteen thousand pounds’.

00:27:00.233 --> 00:27:01.233
I said: ‘That’s it’.

00:27:01.233 --> 00:27:05.922
So I got that money from her.

00:27:05.922 --> 00:27:11.312
I said: ‘All right give Me give Me I’ll
take it, and give it to Guido’.

00:27:11.312 --> 00:27:14.332
I said: ‘Guido go and book your…

00:27:14.332 --> 00:27:18.832
He booked that.

00:27:18.832 --> 00:27:25.883
Then it so happened that, the whole thing
fizzled out, and he got back his money again,

00:27:25.883 --> 00:27:29.522
like a bad penny.

00:27:29.522 --> 00:27:31.763
So we were starting this Shudy Camps.

00:27:31.763 --> 00:27:33.212
I went there.

00:27:33.212 --> 00:27:36.582
Guido said: ‘Mother don’t change your
money.

00:27:36.582 --> 00:27:42.312
I have got all these liras with me.

00:27:42.312 --> 00:27:49.832
All the things that I had to buy were bathroom
fittings and all the, what you call the wc’s

00:27:49.832 --> 00:27:58.123
and all that, plus the, all the marble and
all the curtains and what not, every sort

00:27:58.123 --> 00:27:59.643
of thing.

00:27:59.643 --> 00:28:09.272
And do you know, in one day I did all that,
for such a big place like Shudy, in one day,

00:28:09.272 --> 00:28:10.272
really.

00:28:10.272 --> 00:28:12.282
It was a fast movement.

00:28:12.282 --> 00:28:17.962
And after that, I told them that you pay them
and send Me the bill what ever it is.

00:28:17.962 --> 00:28:22.582
I also gave them hundred pounds more I said:
‘These curtains are very nice also get some

00:28:22.582 --> 00:28:27.003
more for Me maybe, because they’re dark
shade’.

00:28:27.003 --> 00:28:33.462
And can you imagine when the bill came it
was sixteen thousand one hundred pounds.

00:28:33.462 --> 00:28:34.462
Exactly.

00:28:34.462 --> 00:28:38.082
So I had forgotten about hundred.

00:28:38.082 --> 00:28:44.523
I said: ‘How is it sixteen thousand, what
have you done?

00:28:44.523 --> 00:28:45.772
Must be some manipulation’.

00:28:45.772 --> 00:28:49.332
They said: ‘Mother no it’s, grace of God
it has worked out’.

00:28:49.332 --> 00:28:51.532
I said: ‘Then this one hundred from where?’

00:28:51.532 --> 00:28:52.532
‘It’s Yours.

00:28:52.532 --> 00:28:53.532
You gave us.

00:28:53.532 --> 00:28:55.743
You forgot, this is Yours’.

00:28:55.743 --> 00:29:06.513
Then we bought the land and sold it for double
the price and now they have an Ashram.

00:29:06.513 --> 00:29:14.743
But where people are stingy about money, think
about money, things do not work out.

00:29:14.743 --> 00:29:19.503
And also worth knowing, when we bought these
two very big Ashrams in Rome, I don’t know

00:29:19.503 --> 00:29:25.922
if anybody has seen them, here, very big,
two Ashrams we’ve got them.

00:29:25.922 --> 00:29:29.623
That too, I told him just be on the lookout.

00:29:29.623 --> 00:29:39.212
So he said: ‘Mother there is one advertisement
for a house, nearer the main road or something’.

00:29:39.212 --> 00:29:40.763
I said: ‘Main road won’t be good’.

00:29:40.763 --> 00:29:44.813
‘No no it’s quite in the inside but it’s
away from the main city.

00:29:44.813 --> 00:29:47.233
I said: ‘Have you seen it?’

00:29:47.233 --> 00:29:48.233
‘No’.

00:29:48.233 --> 00:29:53.322
I said: ‘I have no time now, you’re telling
Me now, and I have to catch the plane’.

00:29:53.322 --> 00:29:56.952
He said: ‘Mother I had no time to tell You’.

00:29:56.952 --> 00:30:01.423
Luckily that day we heard that the plane was
cancelled because there was some trouble.

00:30:01.423 --> 00:30:04.222
I said: ‘Very good, now we have got one
day’.

00:30:04.222 --> 00:30:12.383
I said: ‘Can you talk to the owner and ask
him if he would like to show Me the place’.

00:30:12.383 --> 00:30:19.262
The owner accepted, and We went there about,
three o’clock, reached there about three.

00:30:19.262 --> 00:30:24.922
My plane was about eight, to India.

00:30:24.922 --> 00:30:32.822
So immediately I saw this, and that amount
which we had spent, I mean, for the buying

00:30:32.822 --> 00:30:36.682
of the land had doubled and we could buy both
the houses.

00:30:36.682 --> 00:30:39.462
And it’s such a big land.

00:30:39.462 --> 00:30:40.472
Immediately I said: ‘Buy it now.’

00:30:40.472 --> 00:30:45.212
We bought it and I caught My plane and went
to India.

00:30:45.212 --> 00:30:52.013
Nobody will believe that in such a short time
we got that beautiful, it’s a very very

00:30:52.013 --> 00:30:56.633
beautiful school, and also very beautiful
area.

00:30:56.633 --> 00:31:02.292
Just see it worked out.

00:31:02.292 --> 00:31:09.302
So I have a feeling that, when you start worrying
about money it slips out somehow, nothing

00:31:09.302 --> 00:31:10.873
works out.

00:31:10.873 --> 00:31:18.152
To feel the grace is to leave everything to
God, now you do it I don’t know.

00:31:18.152 --> 00:31:21.873
You’ll be amazed how things work out.

00:31:21.873 --> 00:31:26.972
It’s beautifully, it works out and you’re
amazed because that’s how you know that

00:31:26.972 --> 00:31:31.613
you have the blessings, how God has blessed
you.

00:31:31.613 --> 00:31:37.092
Money is what, is the dust of His Feet.

00:31:37.092 --> 00:31:44.253
So, I told you when I came these people Customs
troubled Me I said: ‘I don’t know what

00:31:44.253 --> 00:31:52.103
they are going to have now here in recession’.

00:31:52.103 --> 00:31:53.103
But doesn’t matter.

00:31:53.103 --> 00:31:57.163
It’s not going to affect you at all, if
you are in a witness state you can see all

00:31:57.163 --> 00:32:08.402
that, and things will work out, everybody
will have sufficient money, but don’t worry.

00:32:08.402 --> 00:32:13.162
And the more money people have, the more they
are worried about money I have seen that.

00:32:13.162 --> 00:32:18.682
Those who have less in any case they know
that they have less so what is there to worry,

00:32:18.682 --> 00:32:24.912
like Me.

00:32:24.912 --> 00:32:31.993
But about school now, we have three classes
and I’ve already talked to Stephan, let

00:32:31.993 --> 00:32:35.113
him solve the problem.

00:32:35.113 --> 00:32:45.562
If you find anything wrong, you can tell them,
but no parents should go and disturb the teachers,

00:32:45.562 --> 00:32:47.222
absolutely.

00:32:47.222 --> 00:32:52.373
You have no right to do that.

00:32:52.373 --> 00:32:58.103
Even I would say, Indian school.

00:32:58.103 --> 00:33:05.873
Nicely all the people go, stay there this,
in which school is it allowed like this?

00:33:05.873 --> 00:33:10.753
After this, all those who have to see their
children have to stay in a hotel and see them

00:33:10.753 --> 00:33:14.363
only on a particular date which is being told
that you have to see.

00:33:14.363 --> 00:33:15.562
You’ll be disturbing your children all the
time.

00:33:15.562 --> 00:33:23.793
It’s not that anybody can go anytime live
there nicely, and interfere with the working

00:33:23.793 --> 00:33:24.793
of the school.

00:33:24.793 --> 00:33:31.143
We have to bring some system into it, otherwise
your children will suffer.

00:33:31.143 --> 00:33:38.723
Even the Dharamshala school was really absolutely
there were a visitation, of all these bhootish

00:33:38.723 --> 00:33:44.423
people, they tortured the lives of these teachers
there.

00:33:44.423 --> 00:33:47.842
This is never done.

00:33:47.842 --> 00:33:52.503
So now next time, nobody is going to go there
like this.

00:33:52.503 --> 00:33:57.973
I have told him, that if they’re going to
Dharamshala then they should stay in a hostel,

00:33:57.973 --> 00:34:04.293
and the children can also stay with you, not
hostel we can call it a kind of a, inn or

00:34:04.293 --> 00:34:12.523
it is a, can call it, what is it a, it’s
not a big hotel but a kind of a inn sort of

00:34:12.523 --> 00:34:13.523
thing.

00:34:13.523 --> 00:34:18.463
You can take your children there with you,
but you should not go to the school all the

00:34:18.463 --> 00:34:23.513
time, and sit with them, because even there
they have to study.

00:34:23.513 --> 00:34:27.873
The trouble is, Indian standards are very
high.

00:34:27.873 --> 00:34:33.363
All the children, though they have holidays,
only take holidays for one month and the rest

00:34:33.363 --> 00:34:35.433
of the time they are all studying.

00:34:35.433 --> 00:34:42.363
You’ll see how your children will improve,
they don’t know even how to spell c-a-t

00:34:42.363 --> 00:34:44.543
cat.

00:34:44.543 --> 00:34:47.873
Because of the interference of the parents
children are so bad.

00:34:47.873 --> 00:34:55.074
So now if you have real love for your children
allow them to grow properly, and you’ll

00:34:55.074 --> 00:34:56.763
see how they’ll come up.

00:34:56.763 --> 00:35:01.973
Another thing they have no immunity for anything.

00:35:01.973 --> 00:35:08.443
Like if there’s any jaundice, they are the
first to get it, if there’s malaria they

00:35:08.443 --> 00:35:13.183
are the first to get it, if there’s typhoid
they are first to get it.

00:35:13.183 --> 00:35:18.483
While Indian children have that immunity,
because I have seen here also, everybody is

00:35:18.483 --> 00:35:19.483
carrying the child.

00:35:19.483 --> 00:35:23.553
Don’t touch the child all the time.

00:35:23.553 --> 00:35:31.453
Keep the child away from your body, has that,
warmth which goes to the child also.

00:35:31.453 --> 00:35:37.333
Yes sometimes you have to look after the child,
the child must know you love the child, but

00:35:37.333 --> 00:35:41.533
all the time carrying the child like this,
I have seen many ladies who are in my lecture

00:35:41.533 --> 00:35:42.533
also, doing like this.

00:35:42.533 --> 00:35:45.093
Why what is the need?

00:35:45.093 --> 00:35:53.613
You make the child so much conditioned, and
the child cannot remain quiet unless you do

00:35:53.613 --> 00:35:54.973
like this.

00:35:54.973 --> 00:35:57.703
Massage the child nicely.

00:35:57.703 --> 00:35:59.243
Massaging is very good.

00:35:59.243 --> 00:36:02.623
You should massage yourselves also, but at
least the child.

00:36:02.623 --> 00:36:06.053
Let them learn how to take bath everyday.

00:36:06.053 --> 00:36:11.093
Everyday they must be cleansed, so that they
develop the habit of cleanliness.

00:36:11.093 --> 00:36:15.753
They never wash their hands, they don’t
want to wash their hands, and their hands

00:36:15.753 --> 00:36:17.093
smell, they just use paper.

00:36:17.093 --> 00:36:20.253
Whatever you tell them they’ll use paper
never wash their hands.

00:36:20.253 --> 00:36:23.313
The hands smell, mouth smells.

00:36:23.313 --> 00:36:36.723
With all your development, children have no
sense of personal cleanliness.

00:36:36.723 --> 00:36:43.203
We have to know that they’re born-realized
children, and that they have to have, a very

00:36:43.203 --> 00:36:49.063
different type of attitude towards life, as
the same way as the parents have to have,

00:36:49.063 --> 00:36:51.793
a very different attitude towards the school.

00:36:51.793 --> 00:36:58.043
It’s a very patronizing, and you should
be proud that you have such a school here.

00:36:58.043 --> 00:37:05.413
Thank God, they are not in the same mess as
you have been.

00:37:05.413 --> 00:37:08.473
It’s so much protection to them.

00:37:08.473 --> 00:37:15.473
So change your attitude entirely about the
schools, about the children, and look after

00:37:15.473 --> 00:37:18.753
them as if you are their trustees.

00:37:18.753 --> 00:37:26.523
They are in your trust and also, they should
know that you love them very much, as anybody

00:37:26.523 --> 00:37:27.963
else also loves them.

00:37:27.963 --> 00:37:30.533
They must learn how to respect.

00:37:30.533 --> 00:37:32.253
They must have good manners.

00:37:32.253 --> 00:37:37.213
This can be done when the children are here,
because they don’t know how to say namaste,

00:37:37.213 --> 00:37:41.533
they don’t want to say thank you, they don’t
want to say sorry, nothing of the kind.

00:37:41.533 --> 00:37:47.743
All the time they’ll go on asking why, why,
and the Indian teachers start looking, Indian

00:37:47.743 --> 00:37:48.893
children would not.

00:37:48.893 --> 00:37:54.053
Here they have no right to ask.

00:37:54.053 --> 00:37:58.123
They will all be brats here, I tell you all
the children who are going to all these schools

00:37:58.123 --> 00:38:00.753
whether private or to the municipal schools.

00:38:00.753 --> 00:38:06.693
But the other schools that are where there’s,
horrible schools are there here I know.

00:38:06.693 --> 00:38:10.943
Because anybody who comes from those schools,
we don’t want to admit them.

00:38:10.943 --> 00:38:14.733
We have had three of them, we sent them back.

00:38:14.733 --> 00:38:18.103
It’s cheaper all right, but we can’t admit.

00:38:18.103 --> 00:38:21.153
Three children have been sent away.

00:38:21.153 --> 00:38:27.863
If you feel that you must share your money
with your children, then see that they get

00:38:27.863 --> 00:38:31.303
proper education, proper grounding.

00:38:31.303 --> 00:38:37.863
Of course I am going to make a proper complete
sketch of how with the teachers, how to deal

00:38:37.863 --> 00:38:42.733
with the children, how to make them understand,
how to put them into proper way.

00:38:42.733 --> 00:38:47.003
But this is a very important age from three
to five years I think.

00:38:47.003 --> 00:38:51.773
Till one year they should be with the mother
and father.

00:38:51.773 --> 00:38:59.023
But mother should not too much also all the
time, handle the child, and should look after

00:38:59.023 --> 00:39:05.743
the child, in a way as if it is in her trust,
massage the child, look after the child.

00:39:05.743 --> 00:39:08.723
I’ve seen some children just go on crying.

00:39:08.723 --> 00:39:15.193
I don’t know maybe the mothers must have
been very unhappy, when they were bearing

00:39:15.193 --> 00:39:20.433
the child maybe they had a bad time, with
the mother-in-law maybe with the husband whatever

00:39:20.433 --> 00:39:22.473
it is.

00:39:22.473 --> 00:39:26.553
All the time crying.

00:39:26.553 --> 00:39:32.283
All right that can be corrected, but they
are our property and we have to look after

00:39:32.283 --> 00:39:33.283
them.

00:39:33.283 --> 00:39:37.183
But again I say that doesn’t mean, that
a mother should expect others to give bath

00:39:37.183 --> 00:39:42.243
or look after them all the time it’s not
so.

00:39:42.243 --> 00:39:46.333
So I hope you’ll use your discretion now
as far as your children are concerned.

00:39:46.333 --> 00:39:51.873
I am very much concerned about them.

00:39:51.873 --> 00:39:56.623
Now the story goes about, people start talking
like that.

00:39:56.623 --> 00:39:59.543
About the Indian school there’s lot of criticism.

00:39:59.543 --> 00:40:04.673
I would like to know how much you have paid
for the school, to build.

00:40:04.673 --> 00:40:10.873
It’s only your children studying there,
nobody else’s.

00:40:10.873 --> 00:40:14.063
How much money did you pay to buy the land?

00:40:14.063 --> 00:40:15.673
Nobody enquired.

00:40:15.673 --> 00:40:18.313
How much it has cost to build this school?

00:40:18.313 --> 00:40:20.643
Nobody enquired.

00:40:20.643 --> 00:40:33.673
But if you are sending about, ten dollars
for their food and everything.

00:40:33.673 --> 00:40:40.653
Hundred and fifty dollars for four weeks,
where they eat their food, live there, they

00:40:40.653 --> 00:40:44.963
have all facilities, everything, plus their
education.

00:40:44.963 --> 00:40:53.003
But that will be very much discussed.

00:40:53.003 --> 00:41:02.883
You have to know that it’s a very big headache
to teach the western children in India because

00:41:02.883 --> 00:41:13.503
every money has to be accounted for our FERanies
Foreign Exchange Regulations, and every six

00:41:13.503 --> 00:41:23.373
months we have to give the report, to the
Reserve Bank of India, how we are spending

00:41:23.373 --> 00:41:26.763
this foreign exchange.

00:41:26.763 --> 00:41:37.973
And they are experts.

00:41:37.973 --> 00:41:43.343
Despite all that, the people loose-tonguers
are saying: ‘Somebody is eating the money

00:41:43.343 --> 00:41:44.523
there’.

00:41:44.523 --> 00:41:53.923
It’s very difficult, you don’t know, to
manage the western children in India, first

00:41:53.923 --> 00:42:05.483
of all as they are, and then secondly, that
the government is on top of our head, they’re

00:42:05.483 --> 00:42:06.973
sitting.

00:42:06.973 --> 00:42:11.913
Then third is about food.

00:42:11.913 --> 00:42:15.753
Your children are used to tinned foods.

00:42:15.753 --> 00:42:19.573
Like they’ll say we want baked beans in
the morning.

00:42:20.963 --> 00:42:25.513
We want this, we want that, every child wants
something else.

00:42:25.962 --> 00:42:29.615
Now the people will go crazy cooking for all
of them separately.

00:42:29.842 --> 00:42:33.615
You have agreed to such a thing, all right
you want this habit.

00:42:33.862 --> 00:42:38.535
You should not compromise: ‘No, better eat
this’.

00:42:38.081 --> 00:42:40.660
He won’t eat today, he’ll eat tomorrow.

00:42:40.681 --> 00:42:44.840
Whatever is cooked for everybody in the family
please have it.

00:42:45.441 --> 00:42:50.230
And these tinned fruits I am absolutely against
it and I am sure you also don’t want them

00:42:50.281 --> 00:42:51.911
to have tinned fruits.

00:42:52.036 --> 00:42:58.941
They want to have, fried fish and baked beans
and potato chips.

00:42:59.186 --> 00:43:02.356
That’s all they know about food nothing
more, or less.

00:43:05.388 --> 00:43:14.244
So don’t send them any tinned fruits, foods,
tinned fruits.

00:43:14.248 --> 00:43:18.618
I think you better not send them any food,
is a better idea.

00:43:19.342 --> 00:43:23.188
Because if you send them chocolates, their
liver will be spoiled.

00:43:24.261 --> 00:43:30.151
They are getting everything there, so please
if you have to give you can give them clothes

00:43:30.158 --> 00:43:32.931
or anything, but not something to eat.

00:43:33.318 --> 00:43:36.518
Somebody brought lots of chocolates.

00:43:36.581 --> 00:43:38.898
That’s how they got this, problem.

00:43:39.991 --> 00:43:46.501
Chocolates should be avoided for children
up to some age, and also ice cream, but ice

00:43:46.532 --> 00:43:49.841
cream still is not so much fat, but chocolate
specially.

00:43:49.922 --> 00:43:53.022
You can have lollipops and all those things
they are perfectly all right, lollies are

00:43:53.046 --> 00:43:54.046
all right.

00:43:54.206 --> 00:43:58.502
Be careful as to what habits you give to them.

00:43:59.453 --> 00:44:02.996
And tinned food should never be given to children.

00:44:03.023 --> 00:44:04.333
It’s very bad.

00:44:05.003 --> 00:44:10.143
There’s some preservation, and for that
preservation they put some chemicals and that’s

00:44:10.183 --> 00:44:12.753
why the children are very susceptible.

00:44:12.781 --> 00:44:14.523
They have no immunity.

00:44:15.863 --> 00:44:19.091
It’s easy to get fresh things here.

00:44:19.103 --> 00:44:23.011
Not difficult specially in Australia, you
have no problem.

00:44:23.163 --> 00:44:28.953
Get them fresh things, fresh fruits, fresh
food.

00:44:28.978 --> 00:44:30.593
You should give them.

00:44:30.668 --> 00:44:34.073
If you form that habit and not from restaurants
and thing.

00:44:34.268 --> 00:44:39.428
See everything you get it in the market bring
it home, and just shove it into thing and

00:44:39.457 --> 00:44:40.457
give them.

00:44:40.487 --> 00:44:41.487
No.

00:44:41.907 --> 00:44:43.608
For children be careful.

00:44:43.647 --> 00:44:46.778
Once you spoil their stomachs it’s difficult
to make them all right.

00:44:47.656 --> 00:44:54.387
So be very very careful as to what kind of
food you are giving, even if you have to give

00:44:54.426 --> 00:44:57.576
something, then you should read what is in
it you see.

00:44:57.736 --> 00:45:01.636
If there are anything artificial things please
try to avoid.

00:45:03.082 --> 00:45:08.056
These are very precious children we have,
and we have to look after them.

00:45:08.523 --> 00:45:15.813
Again and again I would request you, to be
very kind, to Me by looking after them in

00:45:15.793 --> 00:45:20.793
a proper sensible manner, till they are with
you.

00:45:21.683 --> 00:45:25.173
Also you have to give them some discipline.

00:45:25.242 --> 00:45:26.983
It’s very important.

00:45:27.472 --> 00:45:32.452
By giving them self-esteem: ‘You are Sahaja
Yogis you are this’.

00:45:32.552 --> 00:45:36.342
If you give them, they have no self-esteem
at all.

00:45:36.602 --> 00:45:41.182
If you give them the self-esteem you’ll
be surprised they’ll start behaving very

00:45:41.222 --> 00:45:42.222
well.

00:45:42.452 --> 00:45:49.612
By saying that see: ‘You are special children,
you are Sahaj Yogis, you can’t behave like

00:45:49.639 --> 00:45:52.552
that,’ how they have to be.

00:45:57.637 --> 00:46:02.808
There has to be some discipline, otherwise
at the age of six years you cannot start,

00:46:02.792 --> 00:46:05.938
and even if you start it, it takes some time.

00:46:05.927 --> 00:46:08.532
It’s exhausting, absolutely exhausting.

00:46:08.527 --> 00:46:11.067
Some children are very exhausting.

00:46:13.487 --> 00:46:16.307
So I hope you’ll remember this.

00:46:16.457 --> 00:46:24.237
We have to be kind and nice, discreet, sweet
to them, but first we should know what is

00:46:24.241 --> 00:46:30.411
going to be helpful to them, what is benevolent
for them.

00:46:30.641 --> 00:46:36.021
And just some book comes about children, you
read it, done.

00:46:38.839 --> 00:46:42.449
In Sahaja Yoga you don’t have to read all
such books.

00:46:42.529 --> 00:46:45.039
I’m already going to write and I’ve already
told you these things.

00:46:45.059 --> 00:46:48.029
Just in a wider way, you use your discretion.

00:46:48.409 --> 00:46:52.899
After all you are all realized souls and the
spirit within you, can see in the light of

00:46:52.969 --> 00:46:55.149
that, what is good for your child.

00:46:55.290 --> 00:46:58.629
But avoid tinned food as far as possible.

00:46:58.660 --> 00:47:05.880
Anything tinned is horrible and please don’t
take that for your children.

00:47:05.896 --> 00:47:09.720
I think you people all need not also have
tinned food what is the need?.

00:47:09.996 --> 00:47:14.786
This cancer and all that so rampant, in the
west.

00:47:14.862 --> 00:47:19.236
In India, thank God at least what ever poor
they may be they don’t eat tin food.

00:47:19.221 --> 00:47:20.656
We can’t afford.

00:47:20.821 --> 00:47:26.881
In tin food is more expensive in India than
fresh food, because tin is expensive, luckily.

00:47:32.206 --> 00:47:45.026
All right, so now this is we have done, I
have a little present for your, leader.

